address1: No. 02-10, Blk 1 Ang Mo Kio Industrial Park 2A
longBusinessSummary: KTL Global Limited engages in the distribution and sale of vegetables and fruits in Singapore. It is involved in the import and export of fruits and vegetables; growing of leafy and fruit vegetables; and provision of technical, operational, procurement management, and other related services. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Singapore.
